      "comment": "POPPY'S DARLIN' (6) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (23.42) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning five races. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Better than last start and worth following up. CERULEAN MOON (1) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (23.14) at this track over 400m. Can feature again. SUPER SASSY (8) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at Maitland over 400m behind Despicable Kyro (23.36) in a Grade 5. Can figure in the finish. SOFT WHISPER (3) deserves plenty of thought over this journey.",
